"title": "5257: civil authorities",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5257: civil authorities",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Divinely appointed servants and agents of God exercising their God-given authority for the good of those they govern and punishing those who do wrong, and to whom all must submit.</p>\n<h2>Civil authorities are divinely appointed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:11\">JHN 19:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:17\">1SA 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:1\">1SA 16:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:70-Ps78:71\">PSA 78:70–78:71</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:15-Prov8:16\">PRO 8:15–8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:6\">JER 27:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:10\">JER 43:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:21\">DAN 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:37-Dan2:38\">DAN 2:37–2:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:17\">DAN 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:32\">DAN 4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:18-Dan5:21\">DAN 5:18–5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:26-Dan5:28\">DAN 5:26–5:28</a></p>\n<h2>Civil authorities are God's servants and agents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:4\">ROM 13:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:1\">ISA 45:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:9\">JER 25:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:6\">JER 27:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:10\">JER 43:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:6\">ROM 13:6</a></p>\n<h2>Civil authority exercised for the good of all and in order to punish wrongdoers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:15\">PRO 21:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13-1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:13–2:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:6\">GEN 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:26\">EZR 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:12-Ps72:14\">PSA 72:12–72:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:72\">PSA 78:72</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:12\">PRO 19:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:4\">PRO 29:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:14\">PRO 29:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:11\">ACT 25:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:3-Rom13:4\">ROM 13:3–13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:2\">1TI 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Everyone must submit to civil authorities</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:21-Prov24:22\">PRO 24:21–24:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:1\">TIT 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:2-Eccl8:5\">ECC 8:2–8:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:24-Matt17:27\">MAT 17:24–17:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:15-Matt22:21\">MAT 22:15–22:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:13-Mark12:17\">MRK 12:13–12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:20-Luke20:25\">LUK 20:20–20:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:5-Rom13:7\">ROM 13:5–13:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13-1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:13–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:17\">1PE 2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Civil authorities are only to be obeyed in what is lawful according to Scripture</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:29\">ACT 5:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:17\">EXO 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:2-1Kgs21:3\">1KI 21:2–21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:8\">DAN 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:28\">DAN 3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:7-Dan6:10\">DAN 6:7–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:21\">MAT 22:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:17\">MRK 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:25\">LUK 20:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:19\">ACT 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:23\">HEB 11:23</a></p>",
